    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who appear often on television and are known to the public primarily through that medium. They include actors, announcers, hosts of shows, and religious leaders.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
